14
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:51,360
Let me give you a very specific example of an investment

15
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:53,690
opportunity.

16
00:00:53,690 --> 00:00:56,060
Suppose a firm invests $100 million

17
00:00:56,060 --> 00:01:01,850
