00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:34,620
in year t plus ROI, this is the profitability

65
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:39,480
of our investments multiplied by the amount that we reinvested,

66
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:42,070
I.

